    "name": "Back in Service: a Metro Driver",
    "steam_appid": 3331320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the adventure and become the master of the metro in a fascinating game that takes you into the mysterious underground world of the Prague capital city. Face challenges on the tracks from the cabin of the historic EČS or 81-71 train. Can you complete the entire route, transport all passengers, and avoid any delays?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/494aa50f6216d46243fbb3d0d640952c.poster.avif?t=1770248749\" width=1170 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/494aa50f6216d46243fbb3d0d640952c.webm?t=1770248749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/494aa50f6216d46243fbb3d0d640952c.mp4?t=1770248749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is not an ordinary train simulator. Here, you have complete freedom to choose what you want to do. Become a train driver and improve your skills, explore the underground tunnels, or help your colleagues with various tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/d6eca63ba15d4613738de95bd8c1e3d6.poster.avif?t=1770248749\" width=1170 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/d6eca63ba15d4613738de95bd8c1e3d6.webm?t=1770248749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/d6eca63ba15d4613738de95bd8c1e3d6.mp4?t=1770248749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If, as a conductor, you prove yourself by completing your route on time according to the schedule, you’ll earn some money. You can then spend it on various items. More ways to spend your earned money will appear in future versions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Likewise, future versions will bring more stations, trains, and tasks!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/f72214c02527d5faf1f4d29200d55dfc.poster.avif?t=1770248749\" width=1170 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/f72214c02527d5faf1f4d29200d55dfc.webm?t=1770248749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/f72214c02527d5faf1f4d29200d55dfc.mp4?t=1770248749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras/ed0db8f5138484b2b37438ccd0626e44.avif?t=1770248749\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331320/extras_big/ed0db8f5138484b2b37438ccd0626e44.avif?t=1770248749 width=800 height=242 /></span></p>",
